article.description: — Jordan Dingle scored 21 points, Clark Slajchert added 16 and Pennsylvania beat Drexel 64-59 on Tuesday night.
article.headline: Penn beats Drexel 64-59
article.story: PHILADELPHIA -- — Jordan Dingle scored 21 points, Clark Slajchert added 16 and Pennsylvania beat Drexel 64-59 on Tuesday night. Lucas Monroe grabbed 11 rebounds for Penn (1-3). Amari Williams led Drexel (1-1) with 20 points and seven rebounds. ------
